1
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:19,791
NETFLIX PREDSTAVLJA

2
00:01:07,916 --> 00:01:14,708
PLAVUŠA

3
00:01:27,541 --> 00:01:30,250
Majka ima iznenađenje za tebe.

4
00:01:32,375 --> 00:01:33,583
Iznenađenje?

5
00:01:34,291 --> 00:01:36,041
Rođendansko iznenađenje.

6
00:01:49,333 --> 00:01:52,291
Norma Jeane. Pogledaj.

7
00:01:53,125 --> 00:01:54,958
Taj je čovjek tvoj otac.

8
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:58,791
Moj otac?

9
00:02:00,291 --> 00:02:01,208
On je moj otac?

10
00:02:02,541 --> 00:02:05,208
Gledaj. Tvoj otac.

11
00:02:12,791 --> 00:02:14,416
Ima lijepo ime.

12
00:02:16,625 --> 00:02:18,000
I poznato ime.

13
00:02:20,125 --> 00:02:21,750
Ime koje ne smijem izreći.

14
00:02:35,541 --> 00:02:36,375
Ne!

15
00:02:39,708 --> 00:02:41,750
Ne diraj prljavim prstima.

16
00:02:44,625 --> 00:02:45,875
Nitko ne zna.

17
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:50,375
I nitko ne smije doznati
da si ovo vidjela.

18
00:02:52,416 --> 00:02:55,083
Mi imamo probleme u svojim životima, znaš?

19
00:02:56,041 --> 00:02:58,791
Kad si se rodila, otac ti je bio daleko.

20
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:03,208
I sad je daleko
i brinem se za njegovu sigurnost.

21
00:03:05,333 --> 00:03:08,375
U našim srcima mi smo vjenčani.

22
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:11,333
Mi smo muž i žena.

23
00:03:14,416 --> 00:03:17,000
Iako odbacujemo
ideju konvencionalnog braka.

24
00:03:19,791 --> 00:03:21,833
Gdje je on?

25
00:03:30,083 --> 00:03:31,291
Ruke mi se tresu.

26
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:36,333
Zar se ova soba trese?

27
00:03:36,416 --> 00:03:37,250
SRETAN ROĐENDAN

28
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:41,375
U Kaliforniji…

29
00:03:42,791 --> 00:03:46,083
Ne možeš znati što je „istina“,
a što je „do tebe“.

30
00:03:56,375 --> 00:03:58,083
Izgleda slasno, zar ne?

31
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,875
Da ne zasliniš posteljinu.

32
00:04:30,375 --> 00:04:33,666
Sjećaš li se, Norma Jeane,
tko je spavao ovdje?

33
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:36,125
U ovoj ladici? Sjećaš li se?

34
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,833
Ti!

35
00:04:42,416 --> 00:04:45,500
Ti, Norma Jeane!
Spavala si upravo u ovoj ladici.

36
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:49,875
Spavala si u ladici,
takvi siromasi smo bili.

37
00:04:53,041 --> 00:04:54,791
Bilo nam je dovoljno, zar ne?

38
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:03,541
CHARLIE CHAPLIN
SVJETLA VELEGRADA

39
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:23,375
<i>Volim te, Norma Jeane.</i>

40
00:05:24,875 --> 00:05:28,541
<i>Jednog dana</i>
<i>vratit ću se u Los Angeles po tebe.</i>

41
00:05:38,041 --> 00:05:41,750
Norma Jeane?

42
00:05:44,333 --> 00:05:45,833
Dušo. Probudi se!

43
00:05:47,833 --> 00:05:48,833
Probudi se!

44
00:05:49,583 --> 00:05:52,000
Hajde. Idemo!

45
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:57,166
-Umorna sam.
-Dođi sa mnom.

46
00:06:03,791 --> 00:06:04,708
U redu.

47
00:06:55,083 --> 00:06:57,583
Ne vrpolji se kao zmija koja mora na WC.

48
00:06:59,916 --> 00:07:04,750
Mama? Što ako kuća izgori?
Zaboravila sam svojeg tigra.

49
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:06,166
Ta igračka.

50
00:07:22,916 --> 00:07:25,750
O, Bože.

51
00:07:25,833 --> 00:07:28,208
Bože, ne vidim ništa.

52
00:07:50,208 --> 00:07:51,583
Što radite?

53
00:07:54,625 --> 00:07:58,166
Pozvane smo u privatnu vilu
na vrhu Laurel Canyona.

54
00:07:58,250 --> 00:08:03,000
Vlasnik ima protupožarnu kuću.
Moja kći i ja bit ćemo sigurne ondje.

55
00:08:03,083 --> 00:08:07,875
Ne smijem reći njegovo ime,
ali vrlo je poznato.

56
00:08:07,958 --> 00:08:09,833
On je velikan industrije.

57
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,333
Ova mu je djevojčica kći.

58
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:16,833
Ovo je grad od pijeska i ništa ne traje,

59
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:18,375
ali mi idemo.

60
00:08:19,375 --> 00:08:20,958
Gospođo, idite kući.

61
00:08:21,041 --> 00:08:23,916
Stavite djevojčicu na spavanje. Kasno je.

62
00:08:26,625 --> 00:08:29,250
Zapravo bih voljela vidjeti pakao izbliza.

63
00:08:30,125 --> 00:08:31,208
Najava.

64
00:08:34,125 --> 00:08:37,291
Gospođo, morate se okrenuti.

65
00:08:37,375 --> 00:08:40,500
Mogu vam dati pratnju,
ali ovo je zapovijed.

66
00:08:40,583 --> 00:08:42,750
Okrenite se ili ću vas uhititi.

67
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:45,416
Zato što vozim svoj automobil?

68
00:08:56,416 --> 00:08:58,833
Žao mi je. Molim vas, nemojte me uhititi.

69
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,875
Da me bar ustrijelite.

70
00:09:13,291 --> 00:09:14,750
Idite kući, dobro?

71
00:09:14,833 --> 00:09:18,375
Pijani ste, drogirani
i večeras nitko nema vremena za ovo.

72
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:21,375
Govorite stvari
koje će vas uvaliti u probleme.

73
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:24,416
Hajde. Idite.

74
00:10:18,416 --> 00:10:21,208
Mama? Je li bio ovdje?

75
00:10:21,291 --> 00:10:24,333
Moj tata? Cijelo ovo vrijeme?

76
00:10:24,416 --> 00:10:26,000
Zašto nas nije posjetio?

77
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,708
Što?

78
00:10:57,458 --> 00:10:58,500
Prevruće je.

79
00:11:03,666 --> 00:11:05,125
Norma Jeane, uđiu kadu.

80
00:11:06,291 --> 00:11:08,083
Budi dobra curica i uđi.

81
00:11:14,791 --> 00:11:17,333
-Prevruće je.
-Ulazi u kadu!

82
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:25,666
Dobra djevojčica.

83
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:33,041
<i>Voljela je dijete</i>
<i>i htjela ju je poštedjeti boli.</i>

84
00:11:34,833 --> 00:11:39,166
<i>Jer dijete je i samo bilo tajna, otvorena.</i>

85
00:11:46,583 --> 00:11:51,083
<i>Jer djetetov otac</i>
<i>nije želio da se ono rodi.</i>

86
00:11:54,875 --> 00:11:58,750
<i>Jer joj je dao novac,</i>
<i>razbacao novčanice po krevetu.</i>

87
00:12:01,666 --> 00:12:04,250
<i>Jer joj je rekao da je nije volio.</i>

88
00:12:05,208 --> 00:12:06,750
<i>Da je krivo shvatila.</i>

89
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:11,500
<i>Jer prije trudnoće ju je volio.</i>

90
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:16,000
<i>A zatim više nije.</i>

91
00:12:20,291 --> 00:12:23,166
<i>Jer bi se oženio njome. Bila je sigurna.</i>

92
00:12:26,250 --> 00:12:30,166
<i>Jer nitko nije mogao voljeti</i>
<i>tako prokleto dijete.</i>

93
00:12:31,291 --> 00:12:32,541
To je zbog tebe!

94
00:12:33,541 --> 00:12:37,250
Zbog tebe je otišao! Nije te htio!

95
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:51,541
Upomoć! Pomozite nam!

96
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:55,708
Upomoć, mama je bolesna!

97
00:12:55,791 --> 00:12:57,750
-Norma Jeane?
-Pomozite mami.

98
00:12:57,833 --> 00:13:00,125
Clive, uvedi je. Pokrij je.

99
00:13:00,208 --> 00:13:01,708
-Dođi.
-Dođi.

100
00:13:01,791 --> 00:13:03,291
Dođi, Norma Jeane.

101
00:13:03,375 --> 00:13:04,666
Nešto je s mamom?

102
00:13:05,666 --> 00:13:06,875
Treba pomoć.

103
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,958
Treba pomoć?

104
00:13:16,708 --> 00:13:19,083
Pođi unutra sa mnom.

105
00:13:19,166 --> 00:13:22,666
Čekat ćemo ovdje. Dobro?

106
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:24,083
Ostani uz mene.

107
00:13:24,166 --> 00:13:26,500
Sad si dobro.

108
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,875
Na sigurnom si.

109
00:13:35,208 --> 00:13:38,291
<i>Mama je dovoljno dobro</i>
<i>da te sad primi, Norma Jeane.</i>

110
00:13:41,208 --> 00:13:42,916
Mama je pitala za tebe.

111
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,416
Liječnici kažu da je dobro, možeš do nje.

112
00:13:48,541 --> 00:13:49,458
Idemo li?

113
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:55,125
Gdje je ona?

114
00:13:59,333 --> 00:14:00,833
U bolnici u Norwalku.

115
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,125
Je li sad bolje?

116
00:14:08,625 --> 00:14:10,708
Dovoljno dobro da je posjetiš.

117
00:14:23,583 --> 00:14:25,833
Ujak Clive odvest će nas autom,

118
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:29,333
a ja ću ti spakirati nekoliko stvari.

119
00:14:30,250 --> 00:14:31,750
Ti ne moraš ništa.

120
00:14:34,458 --> 00:14:35,291
U redu.

121
00:15:06,458 --> 00:15:09,916
LOS ANGELES - SIROTIŠTE

122
00:15:48,291 --> 00:15:50,041
Oprosti mi, Norma Jeane.

123
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:53,625
Trenutačno nemaš kamo.

124
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:55,583
Majka ti je bolesna.

125
00:15:56,625 --> 00:15:59,000
Liječnici kažu da je jako bolesna.

126
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,875
Htjela te ozlijediti.

127
00:16:03,375 --> 00:16:05,500
Sad ti ne može biti majka.

128
00:16:06,875 --> 00:16:09,750
Ni ja ti sad ne mogu biti majka.

129
00:16:12,250 --> 00:16:13,916
Ali ja nisam siroče.

130
00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:17,541
Imam mamu i tatu.

131
00:16:18,458 --> 00:16:19,791
Ja nisam siroče.

132
00:16:20,541 --> 00:16:24,125
Moj tata uskoro se vraća. Obećao je.

133
00:16:26,375 --> 00:16:30,500
Hajde, Norma Jeane. Budi dobra djevojčica.

134
00:16:30,583 --> 00:16:31,416
Ne!

135
00:16:33,583 --> 00:16:35,541
Molim te, Norma Jeane.

136
00:16:35,625 --> 00:16:37,125
-Ne!
-Prestani!

137
00:16:37,208 --> 00:16:38,708
-Nisam siroče!
-Hajde!

138
00:16:38,791 --> 00:16:40,666
Hajde! Budi dobra djevojčica.

139
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,833
Nisam siroče!

140
00:16:43,666 --> 00:16:46,291
Barem donesi kovčege, Clive, dovraga!

141
00:16:46,375 --> 00:16:50,208
Tata se ubrzo vraća! Obećao je!

142
00:16:50,291 --> 00:16:51,833
Ne. Prestani!

143
00:16:51,916 --> 00:16:53,250
Prestani plakati!

144
00:16:53,333 --> 00:16:56,666
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

145
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:59,583
<i>Da bude bezbrižno</i>

146
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:05,750
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

147
00:17:05,833 --> 00:17:09,958
<i>A gdje je moj ?</i>

148
00:17:10,041 --> 00:17:14,250
<i>Bogat ili siromašan, nije me briga</i>

149
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:19,416
<i>Ako nema milijun, bit će dosta i pola</i>

150
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:23,208
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

151
00:17:23,291 --> 00:17:26,666
<i>Jesi li ti moj ta-tata ?</i>

152
00:17:28,708 --> 00:17:31,458
<i>Krug svjetlosti je vaš.</i>

153
00:17:32,333 --> 00:17:35,291
To je krug svjetlosti i pozornosti.

154
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:41,500
Zatvorite se u krug.

155
00:17:44,583 --> 00:17:47,541
Nosite ga svugdje sa sobom.

156
00:17:48,458 --> 00:17:51,875
Zamislit ćete da se uz vaše fizičko tijelo

157
00:17:51,958 --> 00:17:54,750
nalazi zamišljeno tijelo vašeg lika,

158
00:17:54,833 --> 00:17:56,625
<i>kojeg ste stvorili svojim umom.</i>

159
00:17:57,666 --> 00:18:01,333
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

160
00:18:01,416 --> 00:18:05,458
<i>Sa sjedinama u kosi</i>

161
00:18:06,375 --> 00:18:09,791
Tatice, nisam znala što odjenuti.

162
00:18:09,875 --> 00:18:11,625
Lijepo izgledaš.

163
00:18:12,250 --> 00:18:13,250
Jesi li siguran?

164
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:16,208
Jako sam nervozna.

165
00:18:16,291 --> 00:18:19,416
Nemoj zakasniti na sastanak u 17 h.

166
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:23,000
Kao da bih mogla. Bože.

167
00:18:25,375 --> 00:18:27,500
Zar ne vidiš, Norma Jeane?

168
00:18:27,583 --> 00:18:30,750
Budućnost ti je na dlanu.

169
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:35,958
<i>Marilyn Monroe za g. Z-a?</i>

170
00:18:43,083 --> 00:18:48,125
<i>„Zamisli da svaku večer znaš</i>

171
00:18:48,208 --> 00:18:50,875
<i>da te stotine raznih ljudi voli.“</i>

172
00:18:51,583 --> 00:18:52,875
<i>„Žele tebe.“</i>

173
00:18:53,916 --> 00:18:55,041
„Ti pripadaš.“

174
00:18:57,291 --> 00:18:59,750
„Već je to dovoljno.“

175
00:19:22,791 --> 00:19:24,833
„Nosiš ga uvijek sa sobom.“

176
00:19:25,791 --> 00:19:27,375
„Krug svjetlosti je tvoj.“

177
00:19:27,458 --> 00:19:33,041
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>
<i>Ako naiđe na probleme</i>

178
00:19:33,125 --> 00:19:35,125
PREDSJEDNIK - PRIVATNO

179
00:19:35,916 --> 00:19:39,833
<i>Svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

180
00:19:39,916 --> 00:19:43,333
<i>Da ga čuva</i>

181
00:19:43,416 --> 00:19:47,958
<i>Osjećamo se kao Crvenkapica</i>

182
00:19:48,041 --> 00:19:50,166
<i>Jer vukovi su jako gladni…</i>

183
00:19:50,250 --> 00:19:51,375
<i>Ne moraš čitati.</i>

184
00:19:52,916 --> 00:19:54,208
Ne razumijem.

185
00:19:55,166 --> 00:19:59,083
Upala si. Glumiš u filmu.
Ako se zoveš Marilyn Monroe.

186
00:20:01,083 --> 00:20:02,333
Da, to sam ja.

187
00:20:03,333 --> 00:20:05,291
Ali ne razumijem.

188
00:20:06,166 --> 00:20:09,791
<i>Vidiš li onog čovjeka?</i>
<i>To je Max Fabian, producent.</i>

189
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:11,708
<i>Idi i pobrini se za sebe.</i>

190
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:15,083
<i>Zašto uvijek izgledaju</i>
<i>kao nesretni zečevi?</i>

191
00:20:15,166 --> 00:20:18,416
<i>Jer to i jesu. Idi i usreći ga.</i>

192
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:23,333
<i>O, svako dijete treba ta-ta-tatu</i>

193
00:20:23,416 --> 00:20:26,916
<i>Jesi li ti moj ta-tata ?</i>

194
00:20:27,833 --> 00:20:31,625
<i>Jesi li ti moj ta-tata ?</i>

195
00:20:36,041 --> 00:20:39,125
<i>U redu je, Norma Jeane. Vrati se.</i>

196
00:20:39,208 --> 00:20:40,833
<i>Vrati se, Norma Jeane.</i>

197
00:20:46,375 --> 00:20:49,833
Hej, dobro je.

198
00:20:50,708 --> 00:20:51,708
U redu je.

199
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:04,708
Dobro je.

200
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:19,375
Sve je u redu.

201
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:23,500
Hej. Sve je u redu.

202
00:21:26,541 --> 00:21:31,041
Norma Jeane? O čemu si razmišljala?

203
00:21:33,958 --> 00:21:35,250
Nisam razmišljala.

204
00:21:40,875 --> 00:21:41,791
Možda…

205
00:21:44,458 --> 00:21:47,083
sam se prisjećala?

206
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:52,166
PROBNA SNIMKA
PRODUCENT

207
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:54,041
LIK - NELL
6.12.1951.

208
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:12,291
Pročitala sam cijeli scenarij.

209
00:22:13,625 --> 00:22:18,916
Tako je tako čudna, uznemirujuća priča.

210
00:22:20,125 --> 00:22:23,833
Mentalno nestabilna žena
koja gotovo ubije djevojčicu.

211
00:22:25,666 --> 00:22:29,291
Kao roman od Dostojevskoga
gdje imaš simpatije prema zločincu

212
00:22:30,125 --> 00:22:31,875
i ne želiš da je kazne.

213
00:22:33,833 --> 00:22:36,416
Čitala si Dostojevskog, dušo?

214
00:22:38,666 --> 00:22:39,708
U redu.

215
00:22:46,166 --> 00:22:49,041
Dobro, gđice Monroe, krenimo.

216
00:23:02,583 --> 00:23:03,583
Gđice Monroe?

217
00:23:39,041 --> 00:23:42,041
Vrati se nazad. Idi.

218
00:23:43,083 --> 00:23:44,166
„Ona je tvoja?“

219
00:23:45,166 --> 00:23:48,500
Ne. Ne pripada mi.

220
00:23:50,208 --> 00:23:53,916
Ovo nije tvoja soba.
Vrati se ondje i idi spavati.

221
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:55,833
„Ona plače.“

222
00:23:57,666 --> 00:23:59,875
Prestanu ako ne obraćaš pažnju.

223
00:24:04,291 --> 00:24:08,541
„Idem prije no što blizanci
iskoče iz ormara.“

224
00:24:14,250 --> 00:24:16,333
Ali sad nemaš razloga za odlazak.

225
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:21,500
„Naravno da imam. Želim to.“

226
00:24:24,916 --> 00:24:26,125
Idem s tobom.

227
00:24:27,541 --> 00:24:30,833
-Idemo na ples.
-„Što nije u redu s tobom?“

228
00:24:31,791 --> 00:24:33,916
„Trebaš biti ovdje s tim djetetom.“

229
00:24:36,291 --> 00:24:37,291
Onda ostani.

230
00:24:39,291 --> 00:24:41,083
Ona te više neće gnjaviti.

231
00:24:42,416 --> 00:24:43,583
„Ti me gnjaviš.“

232
00:24:44,583 --> 00:24:45,958
„Ne mogu te shvatiti.“

233
00:24:54,833 --> 00:24:56,666
Bit ću kakva želiš da budem.

234
00:24:57,958 --> 00:25:02,250
„Zašto ti je to tako bitno?“

235
00:25:02,333 --> 00:25:03,625
Jer…

236
00:25:05,916 --> 00:25:08,541
Pripadam uz tebe, Philipe.

237
00:25:12,958 --> 00:25:15,083
Nisam mislila da ćeš se vratiti.

238
00:25:17,125 --> 00:25:18,250
„Ja sam Jed, Nell.“

239
00:25:20,125 --> 00:25:21,750
„Nisam onaj kojim me smatraš.“

240
00:25:23,666 --> 00:25:24,500
„Sjećaš se?“

241
00:25:25,916 --> 00:25:27,166
„Sjećaš se Philipa?“

242
00:25:33,125 --> 00:25:34,000
Da.

243
00:25:36,416 --> 00:25:40,708
„Sad se prisjeti.“

244
00:25:45,375 --> 00:25:46,375
„Prisjeti se.“

245
00:25:49,583 --> 00:25:52,666
„Kako je izgledao?“

246
00:26:00,125 --> 00:26:01,125
<i>Imao je…</i>

247
00:26:03,916 --> 00:26:05,041
<i>Smeđe oči.</i>

248
00:26:09,041 --> 00:26:10,750
<i>Sjajnu crnu kosu.</i>

249
00:26:21,083 --> 00:26:24,750
„Ja nisam Philip. Ja sam Jed, Nell.

250
00:26:26,291 --> 00:26:27,750
Ja sam Jed.“

251
00:26:31,166 --> 00:26:32,666
Imena ljudi…

252
00:26:35,375 --> 00:26:36,666
Ti nisi on.

253
00:26:41,666 --> 00:26:42,916
Nikad nisi bio.

254
00:26:55,166 --> 00:26:56,666
Hvala, gđice Monroe.

255
00:27:06,666 --> 00:27:07,666
Molim vas.

256
00:27:09,541 --> 00:27:10,708
Mogu li pokušati opet?

257
00:27:16,125 --> 00:27:19,416
Znam da bih mogla biti Nell.

258
00:27:20,916 --> 00:27:22,250
Mislim da sam ja Nell.

259
00:27:23,416 --> 00:27:24,833
Ona hoda u snu.

260
00:27:25,625 --> 00:27:29,583
Ne vidi ga. Vidi svojeg mrtvog zaručnika.

261
00:27:29,666 --> 00:27:31,250
Zarobljena je u zabludi.

262
00:27:33,041 --> 00:27:35,541
Gdje završava sanjarenje,
a počinje ludilo?

263
00:27:37,625 --> 00:27:41,791
Zar nije zabluda osnova ljubavi?

264
00:27:44,916 --> 00:27:46,125
Bilo je predivno…

265
00:27:48,458 --> 00:27:51,875
-Htjela sam…
-Hvala, Johne. Hvala, gospodo.

266
00:27:51,958 --> 00:27:54,541
-To je bilo…
-Javit ćemo se.

267
00:27:54,625 --> 00:27:55,750
<i>Prilično loše, zar ne?</i>

268
00:27:59,625 --> 00:28:00,458
Kao…

269
00:28:02,166 --> 00:28:04,250
da gledaš psihičkog bolesnika.

270
00:28:05,041 --> 00:28:07,666
Nema glume. Nema tehnike.

271
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:11,000
Za takve ljude jasno je
zašto ih privlači gluma.

272
00:28:11,083 --> 00:28:13,875
Jer glumac u svojoj ulozi
uvijek zna tko je.

273
00:28:14,791 --> 00:28:15,958
Što mislite, šefe?

274
00:28:20,833 --> 00:28:21,791
Blagi Bože.

275
00:28:23,458 --> 00:28:25,166
Pogledaj tu guzu.

276
00:28:31,208 --> 00:28:34,500
BOLNICA U NORWALKU

277
00:28:45,083 --> 00:28:47,791
<i>Sigurni ste da je posjet neće uznemiriti?</i>

278
00:28:48,958 --> 00:28:52,208
Vašu majku ili vas, gđice Baker?

279
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:00,250
Nisam je vidjela deset godina.

280
00:29:15,625 --> 00:29:17,750
To su nam problematični pacijenti.

281
00:29:21,208 --> 00:29:22,416
Evo nas.

282
00:29:40,041 --> 00:29:41,250
O, mama.

283
00:30:20,416 --> 00:30:21,500
Mama?

284
00:30:25,833 --> 00:30:29,458
Mama, to sam ja. Norma Jeane.

285
00:31:17,583 --> 00:31:19,500
Majko, ovdje je baš lijepo.

286
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,375
Nije li ovdje lijepo?

287
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,291
Je li ti sad toplije?

288
00:31:49,625 --> 00:31:52,166
Šal ti baš lijepo stoji.

289
00:32:13,375 --> 00:32:16,125
Prošla je godina bila uzbudljiva.

290
00:32:17,250 --> 00:32:20,291
Krasna. Poput bajke.

291
00:32:22,666 --> 00:32:24,416
Ponekad ne mogu vjerovati.

292
00:32:32,208 --> 00:32:34,458
Imam ugovor sa studijem.

293
00:32:35,250 --> 00:32:36,750
U kojem si nekad radila.

294
00:32:38,375 --> 00:32:40,875
Zarađujem za život svojim fotografijama.

295
00:32:57,458 --> 00:33:00,083
Nema Norme Jeane, zar ne?

296
00:33:11,666 --> 00:33:12,666
Mama?

297
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:22,500
Rekla si da je tata radio za studio.

298
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:26,750
Oko 1925.?

299
00:33:31,875 --> 00:33:35,750
Pokušala sam naći
njegovu fotografiju u dokumentima…

300
00:33:35,833 --> 00:33:37,166
Gdje je moja kći?

301
00:33:38,208 --> 00:33:40,000
Rekli su da dolazi.

302
00:33:41,291 --> 00:33:42,708
Ne znam te. Tko si ti?

303
00:34:54,625 --> 00:34:56,208
I rez.

304
00:34:58,833 --> 00:35:03,166
Da, rez. Ne budi kukavica. Rez.

305
00:35:03,250 --> 00:35:04,291
Učini to!

306
00:35:21,791 --> 00:35:22,750
Jesi li dobro?

307
00:35:25,250 --> 00:35:26,708
Hej. Dođi.

308
00:35:27,708 --> 00:35:29,583
Što nije u redu? Jesi li dobro?

309
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:36,500
Dee-Dee, u redu je. Ja ću.
Dobro smo, hvala.

310
00:35:38,916 --> 00:35:40,041
Bože.

311
00:35:42,250 --> 00:35:44,916
Dobro je. Sve je u redu. Hvala.

312
00:35:45,750 --> 00:35:46,750
Pustite nas malo.

313
00:35:50,625 --> 00:35:53,875
<i>„Marilyn Monroe,</i>
<i>nova holivudska zvijezda u usponu</i>

314
00:35:53,958 --> 00:35:57,916
<i>pokazala se kao snažan, dinamičan lik</i>
<i>u ovom mračnom trileru.</i>

315
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,833
<i>Glumi i Richard Widmark.</i>

316
00:35:59,916 --> 00:36:05,416
<i>Njezina izvedba psihički nestabilne</i>
<i>dadilje toliko je jezovito uvjerljiva…”</i>

317
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:10,875
G. Shinne, na premijeri sam
dosta zatvarala oči.

318
00:36:12,083 --> 00:36:14,500
Nisam mogla vjerovati da sam to ja.

319
00:36:15,250 --> 00:36:18,833
Ali svi u publici mislit će da sam Nell.

320
00:36:20,583 --> 00:36:23,958
A Marilyn kasnije na zabavi.

321
00:36:25,208 --> 00:36:26,583
<i>Jesi li na tabletama?</i>

322
00:36:28,708 --> 00:36:30,000
<i>Imaš menstruaciju?</i>

323
00:36:33,291 --> 00:36:34,916
Ne, nemam.

324
00:36:36,750 --> 00:36:38,000
Nije tvoj problem…

325
00:36:38,083 --> 00:36:41,708
<i>Dušo, sljedeći film bit će sjajan,</i>
<i>obećavam ti.</i>

326
00:36:41,791 --> 00:36:44,166
<i>Puno otmjeniji od </i>Ne moraš,

327
00:36:44,250 --> 00:36:47,958
<i>u kojemu je sve osim tebe jeftino sranje,</i>
<i>nemoj me citirati.</i>

328
00:37:08,833 --> 00:37:14,041
AKADEMIJA DRAMSKE UMJETNOSTI, 1952.

329
00:38:13,833 --> 00:38:15,708
<i>Marilyn zaslužuje bolje od ovoga.</i>

330
00:38:18,416 --> 00:38:20,166
Marilyn će biti zvijezda.

331
00:38:26,416 --> 00:38:27,666
Ovo mjesto…

332
00:38:28,958 --> 00:38:30,375
Znaš li na što miriši?

333
00:38:31,833 --> 00:38:34,500
Na staru spermu.

334
00:38:35,750 --> 00:38:39,333
Ništa gorega od ustajale stare sperme.

335
00:38:43,333 --> 00:38:45,708
Nastupali smo u pornićima.

336
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:53,416
-Tek tako. Nije bilo zbog novca.
-Ne odbijam novac. Nikada.

337
00:38:58,208 --> 00:38:59,916
Ona je čistunka.

338
00:39:01,375 --> 00:39:03,708
Gđica Zlatni snovi.

339
00:39:12,333 --> 00:39:14,916
Ljudsko tijelo treba gledati.

340
00:39:22,041 --> 00:39:23,625
Obožavati i…

341
00:39:25,625 --> 00:39:26,583
željeti.

342
00:39:32,250 --> 00:39:37,166
A ne sakrivati kao da je
neka ružna, gnojna rana.

343
00:39:38,208 --> 00:39:40,750
Ima mnogo tijela koja treba sakrivati.

344
00:39:40,833 --> 00:39:43,333
Ali ne tvoje, Cassie, a ni moje.

345
00:39:44,208 --> 00:39:45,916
A svakako ne Normino.

346
00:39:48,791 --> 00:39:50,208
Što radiš?

347
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,416
Gledaš je?

348
00:39:58,166 --> 00:39:59,375
Vidiš li je?

349
00:40:02,666 --> 00:40:04,750
Volim se gledati u zrcalu.

350
00:40:06,666 --> 00:40:09,083
Volim se gledati čak i na WC-u.

351
00:40:12,250 --> 00:40:16,208
Kod nas kući, moj je otac, Chaplin,

352
00:40:17,333 --> 00:40:18,791
bio čaroban.

353
00:40:20,333 --> 00:40:22,208
Privukao bi u sebe svu svjetlost

354
00:40:22,291 --> 00:40:25,041
dok u meni nije ostalo ništa osim tupila.

355
00:40:26,250 --> 00:40:27,250
Kao san.

356
00:40:28,958 --> 00:40:31,291
Mogao sam se vidjeti samo u zrcalu.

357
00:40:33,125 --> 00:40:34,750
Za sve što bih učinio u zrcalu

358
00:40:36,250 --> 00:40:40,125
uslijedili bi mnogi krugovi pljeska.

359
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,708
Gle, Norma Jeane.

360
00:40:51,625 --> 00:40:52,833
Ondje je.

361
00:40:54,833 --> 00:40:56,041
Tvoja prijateljica.

362
00:42:03,791 --> 00:42:05,541
<i>Čekala si nas?</i>

363
00:42:08,666 --> 00:42:09,791
Norma?

364
00:42:13,416 --> 00:42:14,250
Da.

365
00:42:16,083 --> 00:42:17,416
Jesi li gladovala za nama?

366
00:42:19,291 --> 00:42:20,291
Da.

367
00:42:22,250 --> 00:42:24,416
Ne budi draga prema nama.

368
00:42:26,708 --> 00:42:29,166
Da. Kao da hraniš zmiju.

369
00:42:29,875 --> 00:42:32,208
Ja bih na sebi koristio dugačak štap.

370
00:42:40,208 --> 00:42:42,833
<i>Uzmi me, uzmi me</i>

371
00:42:42,916 --> 00:42:45,416
<i>Očaraj me, očaraj me</i>

372
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:48,791
<i>Uzmi me</i>

373
00:42:48,875 --> 00:42:53,375
<i>Ovo je taj tren</i>
<i>Očaraj me</i>

374
00:42:57,416 --> 00:43:00,541
POBJEŠNJELA STRUJA EMOCIJA…

375
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:05,333
KOJU NI PRIRODA NE MOŽE OBUZDATI!

376
00:43:05,416 --> 00:43:10,041
<i>Uzmi me, uzmi me u svoje naručje…</i>

377
00:43:10,583 --> 00:43:13,625
<i>Pjevala je o ljubavi</i>
<i>kao što je i živjela za nju.</i>

378
00:43:13,708 --> 00:43:17,958
<i>Kao Lorelei, razmeće se šarmom</i>
<i>dok zavodi muškarce</i>

379
00:43:18,041 --> 00:43:19,875
<i>na vječno uništenje.</i>

380
00:43:21,208 --> 00:43:24,375
<i>Marilyn Monroe,</i>
<i>vrtoglavi uspon do dramatičnih visina.</i>

381
00:43:24,458 --> 00:43:25,375
KAO ZAVODNICA…

382
00:43:25,458 --> 00:43:27,541
<i>Kad ju je muškarac primio u naručje,</i>

383
00:43:27,625 --> 00:43:28,916
<i>primio je vlastiti život.</i>

384
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:31,125
<i>Smrdiš na jeftin dućan. Znam zašto.</i>

385
00:43:31,708 --> 00:43:33,833
<i>Naravno, nalazim se s nekim.</i>

386
00:43:33,916 --> 00:43:36,458
<i>Bilo s kim, samo da je muškarac.</i>

387
00:43:36,541 --> 00:43:38,666
<i>Joseph Cotten, bespomoćan i očaran njome.</i>

388
00:43:38,750 --> 00:43:40,583
To nije naša Norma.

389
00:43:41,958 --> 00:43:43,875
To nije naša Fishie.

390
00:43:43,958 --> 00:43:47,916
<i>Ali nju nikad neće posjedovati,</i>
<i>kao ni drugi muškarci.</i>

391
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:49,875
<i>I to ga je dovodilo do ludila,</i>

392
00:43:49,958 --> 00:43:53,041
<i>zbog čega je s platna isijavala napetost.</i>

393
00:43:56,416 --> 00:44:03,416
STRASTI KOJE MOGU DOVESTI
MUŠKARCA NA VRH SVIJETA!

394
00:44:03,500 --> 00:44:05,416
ILI GA SUNOVRATITI NA DNO!

395
00:44:11,791 --> 00:44:15,041
NIAGARA I MARILYN MONROE

396
00:44:15,125 --> 00:44:19,125
DVA NAJČAROBNIJA PRIZORA NA SVIJETU!

397
00:44:22,916 --> 00:44:24,916
<i>Zgodna je, rekao bih.</i>

398
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:27,625
Ali to nisam ja, zar ne?

399
00:44:31,791 --> 00:44:33,500
ISTINITA PRIČA

400
00:44:36,916 --> 00:44:38,625
Što kad ljudi doznaju?

401
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:42,333
Dušo, mi smo doznali i još te volimo.

402
00:44:46,791 --> 00:44:49,916
Da se… Da se barem mogu
sakriti u tvojem naručju.

403
00:44:50,875 --> 00:44:52,916
Zauvijek u tvojem naručju.

404
00:44:54,583 --> 00:44:56,291
Ne misliš to, Norma.

405
00:44:57,250 --> 00:44:59,041
Glumica želi biti viđena.

406
00:45:00,541 --> 00:45:04,166
Glumica želi da je voli mnogo ljudi.

407
00:45:04,250 --> 00:45:07,791
Ne. Zaista želim tebe.

408
00:45:10,791 --> 00:45:12,000
Slatka si.

409
00:45:14,083 --> 00:45:16,708
Mrzim ovu. Izgledam kao kreten.

410
00:45:17,708 --> 00:45:20,083
Otvorenih usta, kao da dahćem.

411
00:45:25,875 --> 00:45:28,958
„Otmjeni momci, Charlie Chaplin Jr.

412
00:45:29,583 --> 00:45:32,166
i Edward G. Robinson Jr.“

413
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:37,666
„I plava seks-bomba, Marilyn Monroe.“

414
00:45:38,166 --> 00:45:39,083
„Trojac.“

415
00:45:40,583 --> 00:45:41,833
Kako vulgarno.

416
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,208
„Seks-bomba.“

417
00:45:46,875 --> 00:45:48,416
Što je „seks-bomba“?

418
00:45:49,666 --> 00:45:54,000
Je li ovo seks-bomba?

419
00:45:55,041 --> 00:45:56,250
-Ne!
-Ili ovo?

420
00:45:56,333 --> 00:45:58,875
Ne!

421
00:46:02,416 --> 00:46:03,250
Ne!

422
00:46:03,333 --> 00:46:04,958
STROGO ČUVANA TAJNA:
MONROE U TROJCU

423
00:46:07,458 --> 00:46:09,750
Ne želim da izlaziš s njima u javnost.

424
00:46:15,125 --> 00:46:16,458
A privatno?

425
00:46:20,125 --> 00:46:21,375
Privatno…

426
00:46:24,333 --> 00:46:25,791
Zaštiti se.

427
00:46:25,875 --> 00:46:27,833
G. Shinne, to je tako okrutno.

428
00:46:28,791 --> 00:46:31,916
Grubo i okrutno. I vi… I vi to znate.

429
00:46:32,666 --> 00:46:36,833
Mislim na tvoju karijeru i dobrobit.

430
00:46:38,666 --> 00:46:40,041
Mislite na Marilyn.

431
00:46:40,791 --> 00:46:42,625
-Da.
-Njezinu karijeru.

432
00:46:42,708 --> 00:46:46,125
Da. I njezinu dobrobit.

433
00:46:46,750 --> 00:46:48,583
Ona nema dobrobit.

434
00:46:50,333 --> 00:46:51,666
Ima samo karijeru.

435
00:46:55,625 --> 00:46:57,125
Oni znaju da sam Norma.

436
00:46:58,125 --> 00:46:59,208
Nisam Marilyn.

437
00:47:01,875 --> 00:47:03,500
Razumiju me.

438
00:47:05,041 --> 00:47:08,625
Ja te razumijem. Ja sam te izmislio.

439
00:47:16,500 --> 00:47:18,125
<i>Oh, Norma.</i>

440
00:47:20,875 --> 00:47:22,375
Izgleda da te volim.

441
00:47:24,791 --> 00:47:26,333
Ljubomoran sam na tebe i Eddyja.

442
00:47:28,708 --> 00:47:30,666
Na bilo koga tko te pogleda.

443
00:47:33,958 --> 00:47:36,375
Da mogu voljeti ženu,

444
00:47:37,833 --> 00:47:38,875
to bi bila ti.

445
00:47:41,791 --> 00:47:43,250
Kad kažeš da me voliš…

446
00:47:44,958 --> 00:47:46,208
i kad me pogledaš…

447
00:47:49,291 --> 00:47:52,750
koga vidiš?

448
00:47:53,541 --> 00:47:55,541
Malog Skitnicu? Vidiš li njega?

449
00:47:56,458 --> 00:47:57,416
Ne.

450
00:47:58,958 --> 00:48:00,250
Vidim samo tebe.

451
00:48:05,333 --> 00:48:09,708
Ljudi misle da je blagoslov
biti sin Charlieja Chaplina.

452
00:48:11,333 --> 00:48:14,750
Da je to bajka, a ja sam kraljević.

453
00:48:15,916 --> 00:48:17,541
Ali prokleti smo, Eddy i ja.

454
00:48:21,083 --> 00:48:24,208
Mi smo potomci muškaraca
koji nas nikad nisu htjeli.

455
00:48:29,416 --> 00:48:31,541
Vas dvojica barem imate očeve.

456
00:48:32,916 --> 00:48:34,541
Barem znate tko ste.

457
00:48:37,416 --> 00:48:40,166
Znali smo tko smo i prije rođenja.

458
00:48:42,083 --> 00:48:43,583
Ti ne znaš tko ti je otac.

459
00:48:44,666 --> 00:48:45,875
Ti si slobodna.

460
00:48:47,125 --> 00:48:48,416
Možeš stvoriti samu sebe.

461
00:48:50,708 --> 00:48:52,208
Sviđa mi se tvoje ime.

462
00:48:52,833 --> 00:48:54,375
Marilyn Monroe.

463
00:48:56,916 --> 00:49:00,083
Zvuči izmišljeno. Sviđa mi se.

464
00:49:02,666 --> 00:49:05,083
Kao da si rodila samu sebe.

465
00:49:07,458 --> 00:49:08,875
<i>Zbog njegovih očiju.</i>

466
00:49:09,625 --> 00:49:11,750
<i>Imao je najljepše oči.</i>

467
00:49:12,750 --> 00:49:15,208
<i>Gledao bi me tim očima.</i>

468
00:49:16,041 --> 00:49:18,375
<i>Prodornim, osjećajnim očima.</i>

469
00:49:18,458 --> 00:49:20,958
<i>Sa zida majčina davnašnjeg stana.</i>

470
00:49:23,208 --> 00:49:25,666
<i>Rekao bi kad bi me vidio…</i>

471
00:49:26,583 --> 00:49:28,750
Prepoznao sam te čim sam te ugledao.

472
00:49:31,833 --> 00:49:33,083
Siroče.

473
00:49:34,708 --> 00:49:35,833
Kao ja.

474
00:49:38,166 --> 00:49:39,833
Zatim te majka ostavila…

475
00:49:42,250 --> 00:49:43,458
i osramotila.

476
00:49:44,166 --> 00:49:45,291
Kao i moja.

477
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:49,916
<i>Jer bi me volio</i>
<i>kao što nitko drugi ne bi htio.</i>

478
00:49:51,875 --> 00:49:52,958
<i>Ili ne bi mogao.</i>

479
00:49:54,083 --> 00:49:55,333
<i>Kao blizanac.</i>

480
00:49:56,250 --> 00:49:57,666
<i>S dušom.</i>

481
00:49:57,750 --> 00:49:58,958
Eno Blizanaca.

482
00:50:00,166 --> 00:50:01,166
Vidiš li?

483
00:50:03,083 --> 00:50:04,750
Norma i ja smo Blizanci.

484
00:50:06,416 --> 00:50:07,875
Suđeni blizanci.

485
00:50:12,083 --> 00:50:13,083
Gdje?

486
00:50:13,958 --> 00:50:17,083
-Ne vidim. Gdje?
-Ondje.

487
00:50:22,166 --> 00:50:24,125
Sve je staro milijarde godina.

488
00:50:25,583 --> 00:50:27,208
Nezamislivo beskrajno.

489
00:50:28,625 --> 00:50:30,041
A kako je započelo?

490
00:50:32,041 --> 00:50:35,083
Česticama tako malim
da ih ljudsko oko ni ne vidi.

491
00:50:36,833 --> 00:50:39,500
Vidi ih ondje gore kako blješte.

492
00:50:42,083 --> 00:50:44,458
A ipak, svaka je usamljena.

493
00:50:46,958 --> 00:50:48,250
Pijem u to ime.

494
00:50:53,958 --> 00:50:57,000
Zakunimo se, može? Nas troje.

495
00:50:58,291 --> 00:51:01,291
Da ćemo se zauvijek voljeti kao sada.

496
00:51:02,166 --> 00:51:04,291
Umrijet ćemo jedno za drugo.

497
00:51:06,666 --> 00:51:07,875
Mi smo trokut.

498
00:51:09,458 --> 00:51:12,333
Trokut se ne može
podijeliti na dva dijela.

499
00:51:13,875 --> 00:51:17,541
Mi smo Blizanci, nas troje.

500
00:51:17,625 --> 00:51:20,458
Kao blizanci. Ali troje nas je.

501
00:51:28,000 --> 00:51:29,208
Za Blizance.

502
00:51:33,541 --> 00:51:34,750
Za Blizance.

503
00:52:12,208 --> 00:52:14,541
Bože, znala sam.

504
00:52:16,958 --> 00:52:21,750
Znala sam. Osjećam se naduto i sretno.

505
00:52:23,416 --> 00:52:24,875
Draga moja, zdrava si.

506
00:52:27,041 --> 00:52:28,291
Sve će biti u redu.

507
00:52:31,291 --> 00:52:33,041
Sretna sam.

508
00:52:34,250 --> 00:52:36,375
Želim ovo dijete.

509
00:52:36,458 --> 00:52:39,250
Suprug i ja pokušavamo već godinama.

510
00:52:50,500 --> 00:52:51,500
Hej, Norma.

511
00:52:55,041 --> 00:52:59,125
Što je bilo? Izgledaš krhko. I sretno.

512
00:53:06,541 --> 00:53:07,625
O, Norma…

513
00:53:09,791 --> 00:53:10,916
Misliš da jesi?

514
00:53:15,291 --> 00:53:17,375
-Je li to ono što ja mislim?
-Da!

515
00:53:18,458 --> 00:53:19,875
Čovječe!

516
00:53:24,083 --> 00:53:25,458
Jeste li sretni zbog mene?

517
00:53:27,416 --> 00:53:30,041
Mi? Blizanci?

518
00:53:34,041 --> 00:53:35,541
-Da!
-Da!

519
00:53:45,208 --> 00:53:46,541
Kao u filmovima.

520
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:50,666
Tako nešto događa se samo u filmovima.

521
00:53:50,750 --> 00:53:51,625
Što?

522
00:53:54,416 --> 00:53:55,666
Taj tigrić.

523
00:54:03,333 --> 00:54:04,791
Imala sam jednog takvog.

524
00:54:06,000 --> 00:54:08,208
Davno, kad sam bila djevojčica.

525
00:54:09,750 --> 00:54:11,208
Djetetova prva igračka.

526
00:54:12,916 --> 00:54:13,750
Slatko.

527
00:54:16,500 --> 00:54:19,500
Casse, gdje nas vodiš?

528
00:54:21,000 --> 00:54:22,333
Želim ići kući.

529
00:54:23,916 --> 00:54:24,916
Je li tako?

530
00:54:26,250 --> 00:54:27,750
Bebi se spava.

531
00:54:30,250 --> 00:54:32,916
Ovo je pogled koji Beba treba vidjeti.

532
00:54:34,541 --> 00:54:35,541
Samo pričekaj.

533
00:54:44,416 --> 00:54:49,625
Norma, možeš gledati ili ne…

534
00:54:51,500 --> 00:54:52,958
ali ondje je.

535
00:54:56,041 --> 00:54:57,500
-Marilyn.
-Marilyn.

536
00:55:08,708 --> 00:55:12,500
<i>Ne mogu prihvatiti ulogu. Oprosti.</i>

537
00:55:16,125 --> 00:55:17,458
<i>Jesi li još na liniji?</i>

538
00:55:19,125 --> 00:55:20,333
<i>Nešto nije u redu?</i>

539
00:55:21,083 --> 00:55:26,458
<i>Ne, sve je u redu. Samo ne mogu. Ne sada.</i>

540
00:55:27,250 --> 00:55:30,791
<i>Ne sada? Zašto ne sada?</i>

541
00:55:33,291 --> 00:55:37,000
<i>Ti si najnovija senzacija na blagajnama.</i>

542
00:55:37,875 --> 00:55:42,958
<i>Zanuck je zbog tebe kupio prava</i>
<i>na </i>Muškarci više vole plavuše<i>.</i>

543
00:55:43,041 --> 00:55:46,666
<i>Želi te pokazati u tom filmu.</i>

544
00:55:50,458 --> 00:55:51,750
Koliko bih dobila?

545
00:55:56,708 --> 00:55:58,000
<i>Prema ugovoru.</i>

546
00:55:59,541 --> 00:56:00,791
<i>Pet stotina tjedno.</i>

547
00:56:05,208 --> 00:56:07,291
Koliko bi dobila Jane Russell?

548
00:56:09,208 --> 00:56:10,416
<i>Ugovor se razmatra.</i>

549
00:56:11,250 --> 00:56:13,500
<i>Treba je unajmiti od drugog studija.</i>

550
00:56:16,375 --> 00:56:17,875
Koliko?

551
00:56:19,458 --> 00:56:21,916
<i>-Brojke nisu konačne.</i>
-Koliko?

552
00:56:24,583 --> 00:56:29,166
<i>Traže 100 000 dolara.</i>

553
00:56:32,416 --> 00:56:34,083
100 000 dolara?

554
00:56:39,125 --> 00:56:43,416
Ja dobijem 5000,
a Jane Russell 100 000 dolara?

555
00:56:44,000 --> 00:56:48,500
A ja glumim plavušu
u <i>Muškarci više vole plavuše?</i>

556
00:56:50,375 --> 00:56:51,625
To je uvredljivo.

557
00:56:53,458 --> 00:56:56,958
-Sad ću prekinuti. Doviđenja.
<i>-Marilyn, čekaj.</i>

558
00:56:57,041 --> 00:56:59,208
Jebeš Marilyn. Ona nije ovdje.

559
00:57:26,875 --> 00:57:28,208
<i>Mojoj Bebi.</i>

560
00:57:30,416 --> 00:57:31,416
<i>U tebi</i>

561
00:57:32,916 --> 00:57:38,291
<i>Novi svijet se rađa</i>

562
00:57:40,958 --> 00:57:47,333
<i>Prije tebe nije bilo nikoga</i>

563
00:57:49,875 --> 00:57:51,958
Želiš li postati baka?

564
00:57:54,375 --> 00:57:55,541
Koja je ovo godina?

565
00:57:56,833 --> 00:57:58,458
U koje smo doba otputovali?

566
00:58:01,375 --> 00:58:03,916
Mama, sad je svibanj 1953.

567
00:58:06,125 --> 00:58:07,333
Ja sam Norma Jeane.

568
00:58:08,375 --> 00:58:10,000
Došla sam te čuvati.

569
00:58:12,291 --> 00:58:13,708
Kosa ti je tako bijela.

570
00:58:24,500 --> 00:58:28,333
Kad si me rodila, nisi bila udana.

571
00:58:29,291 --> 00:58:31,708
Nisi imala muškarca da te uzdržava.

572
00:58:33,500 --> 00:58:34,916
I rodila si dijete.

573
00:58:45,666 --> 00:58:46,958
To je bilo hrabro.

574
00:58:50,416 --> 00:58:51,833
Neka druga bi ga se…

575
00:58:54,750 --> 00:58:58,083
znaš, riješila.

576
00:58:59,833 --> 00:59:00,791
Mene.

577
00:59:03,958 --> 00:59:08,333
I ja ne bih bila ovdje.
Ne bi postojala Marilyn.

578
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:13,250
A ona postaje poznata.

579
00:59:15,458 --> 00:59:17,625
Pisma obožavatelja, telegrami…

580
00:59:19,208 --> 00:59:20,791
cvijeće od stranaca.

581
00:59:36,750 --> 00:59:38,125
Ali ti si bila hrabra.

582
00:59:44,291 --> 00:59:45,916
Učinila si ispravnu stvar.

583
00:59:49,625 --> 00:59:51,000
Rodila si dijete.

584
00:59:56,041 --> 00:59:57,041
Rodila si mene.

585
01:00:01,708 --> 01:00:03,875
<i>Ona ima tajanstvenu bolest.</i>

586
01:00:09,000 --> 01:00:10,958
Bolest koju nitko ne razumije.

587
01:00:12,833 --> 01:00:14,166
Sindrom simptoma.

588
01:00:22,708 --> 01:00:24,125
Je li nasljedno?

589
01:00:25,458 --> 01:00:26,458
Oprostite?

590
01:00:30,500 --> 01:00:33,625
Bolest moje mame, je li…

591
01:00:36,291 --> 01:00:37,500
Je li…

592
01:00:38,666 --> 01:00:40,625
Je li to nešto s čime se rodiš?

593
01:01:05,500 --> 01:01:09,041
<i>U redu, Marilyn, sad ću te predati Yvet.</i>

594
01:01:09,125 --> 01:01:11,916
<i>Sjećaš li se Yvet? Pomoći će ti.</i>

595
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:13,416
<i>Marilyn?</i>

596
01:01:15,916 --> 01:01:20,916
-Očajnički trebam pomoć.
<i>-Draga, sve ću dogovoriti.</i>

597
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:24,208
<i>Računaj sutra ujutro u 8 h.</i>
<i>Netko će doći po tebe.</i>

598
01:02:21,125 --> 01:02:22,458
Želim se vratiti.

599
01:02:30,083 --> 01:02:32,208
Hej, predomislila sam se.

600
01:02:33,666 --> 01:02:35,333
Imam se pravo predomisliti.

601
01:02:40,208 --> 01:02:41,750
Blještava svjetla.

602
01:02:52,458 --> 01:02:54,125
U dobrim si rukama, draga.

603
01:02:57,708 --> 01:03:01,375
Zar me ne čujete? Predomislila sam se.

604
01:03:10,291 --> 01:03:12,208
Nemojte. Zar me ne čujete?

605
01:03:15,458 --> 01:03:18,375
Ovo će vas uspavati.

606
01:03:19,833 --> 01:03:22,041
Ne, želim se vratiti.

607
01:03:39,625 --> 01:03:42,166
Ne. Čekajte.

608
01:03:42,750 --> 01:03:45,583
Čekajte! Ne!

609
01:03:47,125 --> 01:03:48,125
Norma!

610
01:03:51,458 --> 01:03:52,291
Ne!

611
01:04:59,666 --> 01:05:00,791
Gđice Monroe?

612
01:05:03,500 --> 01:05:07,750
<i>Zbogom, dijete</i>

613
01:05:09,125 --> 01:05:13,041
<i>Zapamti da si moje dijete</i>

614
01:05:13,125 --> 01:05:13,958
Gđice Monroe.

615
01:05:17,125 --> 01:05:18,916
Gđice Monroe, vrijeme je.

616
01:05:26,166 --> 01:05:30,083
<i>Bila sam usamljena</i>

617
01:05:33,000 --> 01:05:33,916
Gđice Monroe?

618
01:05:38,125 --> 01:05:44,750
<i>Neće biti nikog drugog</i>

619
01:05:45,666 --> 01:05:47,583
<i>Ja sam jedan od dobitnika.</i>

620
01:05:48,708 --> 01:05:50,958
<i>Svjestan sam toga. I zahvalan.</i>

621
01:05:52,041 --> 01:05:55,541
Ne uzimam to zdravo za gotovo.
Baseball je bio moj život.

622
01:05:56,416 --> 01:05:57,916
Baseball je bio moja karta.

623
01:05:58,500 --> 01:06:00,250
A sad…

624
01:06:01,333 --> 01:06:02,291
U mirovini sam.

625
01:06:03,083 --> 01:06:05,333
Imam puno posla, sponzorstva i…

626
01:06:06,416 --> 01:06:09,916
nastupa, sastanaka savjetodavnog odbora.

627
01:06:14,500 --> 01:06:16,166
Zvučim kao budala.

628
01:06:16,791 --> 01:06:19,333
Ne.

629
01:06:20,583 --> 01:06:23,083
Sigurno je čudno biti…

630
01:06:24,416 --> 01:06:25,250
pa…

631
01:06:26,916 --> 01:06:28,541
heroj.

632
01:06:33,666 --> 01:06:35,541
Ne izgledaš umirovljeno.

633
01:06:36,708 --> 01:06:38,916
Puno se pojavljuješ u novinama.

634
01:06:39,708 --> 01:06:42,916
Ni upola koliko ti, Marilyn.

635
01:06:45,041 --> 01:06:46,041
Tko, ja?

636
01:06:47,916 --> 01:06:48,916
Pa…

637
01:06:51,125 --> 01:06:53,166
To je studijska promidžba.

638
01:06:56,125 --> 01:06:57,375
Grozni su.

639
01:06:59,791 --> 01:07:01,291
Što sve izmišljaju.

640
01:07:03,333 --> 01:07:05,458
Znam da bih se trebala naviknuti.

641
01:07:08,375 --> 01:07:09,708
Ali ne mogu.

642
01:07:11,750 --> 01:07:13,041
Zaista boli.

643
01:07:21,541 --> 01:07:23,291
Kako si ti krenula?

644
01:07:37,083 --> 01:07:38,083
Krenula?

645
01:07:38,875 --> 01:07:40,041
U filmovima.

646
01:07:41,166 --> 01:07:42,125
S glumom.

647
01:07:50,291 --> 01:07:51,500
Ne znam.

648
01:07:57,250 --> 01:07:58,083
Ja…

649
01:07:59,166 --> 01:08:00,375
Mislim da…

650
01:08:10,625 --> 01:08:12,208
Mislim da sam otkrivena.

651
01:08:15,000 --> 01:08:16,291
Kako otkrivena?

652
01:08:28,541 --> 01:08:30,041
Mogli bismo otići.

653
01:08:33,083 --> 01:08:35,125
Bojim se nekih ljudi ovdje.

654
01:08:42,833 --> 01:08:43,833
Hej.

655
01:08:46,750 --> 01:08:48,291
Znam kako je…

656
01:08:51,166 --> 01:08:52,375
biti usamljen,

657
01:08:54,916 --> 01:08:56,333
htjeti bolji život.

658
01:08:58,083 --> 01:08:59,791
Dobar, jednostavan život.

659
01:09:01,750 --> 01:09:03,166
Pristojan život.

660
01:09:11,625 --> 01:09:13,791
Želim krenuti ispočetka.

661
01:09:16,166 --> 01:09:17,416
Želim živjeti u…

662
01:09:18,750 --> 01:09:22,791
Želim živjeti u drugom svijetu.
Daleko od Hollywooda.

663
01:09:24,291 --> 01:09:25,708
Želim živjeti u…

664
01:09:29,458 --> 01:09:30,625
Čehov!

665
01:09:34,500 --> 01:09:36,291
Želim se preseliti u New York.

666
01:09:39,791 --> 01:09:41,083
Studirati glumu.

667
01:09:42,916 --> 01:09:44,625
Ozbiljnu glumu.

668
01:09:44,708 --> 01:09:47,291
U filmovima te izrežu na komadiće.

669
01:09:47,375 --> 01:09:51,041
Rez, rez, rez. Kao <i>puzzle.</i>

670
01:09:51,125 --> 01:09:53,000
Ali ti ne sastavljaš dijelove.

671
01:09:55,416 --> 01:09:57,458
Ti živiš u ulozi.

672
01:09:57,541 --> 01:10:01,416
U njemu si svake večeri
do spuštanja zavjese.

673
01:10:17,041 --> 01:10:18,458
Ali uglavnom…

674
01:10:23,375 --> 01:10:24,791
želim se smiriti.

675
01:10:26,666 --> 01:10:27,916
Kao i svaka djevojka.

676
01:10:28,958 --> 01:10:30,375
Imati obitelj.

677
01:10:34,041 --> 01:10:35,791
Jako volim djecu.

678
01:10:37,458 --> 01:10:39,458
Luda sam za njima.

679
01:10:45,375 --> 01:10:46,791
<i>Je li netko umro?</i>

680
01:10:50,291 --> 01:10:51,500
Što je sve ovo?

681
01:10:53,583 --> 01:10:54,916
Ovo cvijeće.

682
01:10:58,291 --> 01:10:59,500
Jesam li leš?

683
01:11:00,333 --> 01:11:01,833
Je li ovo mrtvačnica?

684
01:11:05,166 --> 01:11:07,833
<i>Ja sam robinja toj Marilyn Monroe.</i>

685
01:11:08,750 --> 01:11:11,291
Prijavila sam se za raskoš,

686
01:11:11,375 --> 01:11:14,583
ali kao Lorelei Lee,
trudim se održati na površini.

687
01:11:17,333 --> 01:11:20,750
Gđice Monroe, ne mislite ni riječ od toga.

688
01:11:21,666 --> 01:11:23,833
Da niste Marilyn, tko biste bili?

689
01:11:24,875 --> 01:11:26,333
Gđice Monroe, okrutni ste.

690
01:11:27,458 --> 01:11:30,416
Svatko na svijetu

691
01:11:30,500 --> 01:11:33,750
dao bi desnu ruku da bude na vašem mjestu
i vi to znate.

692
01:11:37,125 --> 01:11:38,041
Znam.

693
01:11:39,958 --> 01:11:44,916
„Marilyn, ti si naslovnica
svakog mjeseca.“

694
01:11:46,708 --> 01:11:50,166
„Marilyn, ti si kurva plavuša.“

695
01:11:50,250 --> 01:11:54,791
„Nitko te nikad neće voljeti,
odvratna skitnice.“

696
01:11:54,875 --> 01:12:00,333
„Makni se s radija,
televizije i iz naših filmova.“

697
01:12:00,416 --> 01:12:02,083
„Truješ našu djecu.“

698
01:12:02,833 --> 01:12:03,833
„Nisam obožavatelj.“

699
01:12:07,750 --> 01:12:08,958
Kao filmski kritičari.

700
01:12:10,625 --> 01:12:13,666
Neki vole Marilyn, neki je mrze.

701
01:12:15,875 --> 01:12:17,500
Kakve to veze ima sa mnom?

702
01:12:18,416 --> 01:12:21,666
Da, ona je kurva mjeseca.

703
01:12:21,750 --> 01:12:23,666
-Whitey!
-Ona je slatka kurvica.

704
01:12:24,625 --> 01:12:27,125
<i>Napisat ću pismo i zalijepiti marku</i>

705
01:12:28,791 --> 01:12:32,583
Gđice Monroe, ovo je povjerljivo pismo.

706
01:12:35,458 --> 01:12:38,166
Ima palicu umjesto kurca. Oprosti.

707
01:12:43,583 --> 01:12:44,708
„Draga Norma Jeane.

708
01:12:45,708 --> 01:12:49,208
Ovo je najteže pismo
koje sam ikada napisao.“

709
01:12:49,875 --> 01:12:55,250
<i>Iskreno, ne znam zašto ti se javljam</i>
<i>nakon toliko godina.</i>

710
01:12:55,333 --> 01:12:58,375
<i>Imao sam srčani udar</i>

711
01:12:58,458 --> 01:13:01,083
<i>i ozbiljno sam razmislio o životu.</i>

712
01:13:01,833 --> 01:13:05,416
<i>Ne ponosim se svojim ponašanjem.</i>

713
01:13:06,541 --> 01:13:07,375
To je on.

714
01:13:07,916 --> 01:13:10,541
<i>„Ja sam tvoj otac, Norma Jeane.</i>

715
01:13:12,291 --> 01:13:14,166
<i>Preda mnom stoji</i>

716
01:13:14,250 --> 01:13:19,083
<i>intervju s Marilyn Monroe</i>
<i>u novom </i>Pageantu.

717
01:13:20,041 --> 01:13:21,958
<i>Navrle su mi suze na oči.</i>

718
01:13:23,166 --> 01:13:25,541
<i>Rekla si da ti je majka hospitalizirana</i>

719
01:13:25,625 --> 01:13:27,458
<i>i da ne poznaješ svojeg oca.</i>

720
01:13:28,875 --> 01:13:31,916
<i>Iako ga svaki čas očekuješ.</i>

721
01:13:33,333 --> 01:13:34,791
<i>Jadna moja kćeri.”</i>

722
01:13:36,166 --> 01:13:37,416
O, Bože.

723
01:13:38,416 --> 01:13:39,458
<i>„Nisam znao.”</i>

724
01:13:39,541 --> 01:13:40,708
To je on.

725
01:13:42,958 --> 01:13:43,958
Znala sam.

726
01:13:45,875 --> 01:13:47,958
Gledao me sve ove godine.

727
01:13:49,583 --> 01:13:50,708
Osjećala sam.

728
01:13:52,125 --> 01:13:55,791
<i>„Uskoro ću ti se javiti uživo,</i>
<i>Norma Jeane.</i>

729
01:13:57,083 --> 01:13:59,958
<i>Čekaj me, dragocjena kćeri…</i>

730
01:14:01,791 --> 01:14:03,750
<i>do posebne prigode u životu…</i>

731
01:14:04,708 --> 01:14:08,625
<i>kad će otac i kći proslaviti</i>
<i>dugo uskraćenu ljubav.</i>

732
01:14:10,708 --> 01:14:11,708
<i>Tvoj uplakani tata.”</i>

733
01:14:12,958 --> 01:14:15,750
<i>Marilyn!</i>

734
01:14:15,833 --> 01:14:22,833
MUŠKARCI VIŠE VOLE PLAVUŠE

735
01:14:30,000 --> 01:14:32,708
Marilyn!

736
01:14:34,583 --> 01:14:37,000
Imate li trenutak, molim vas? Hvala.

737
01:14:44,583 --> 01:14:48,125
Marilyn!

738
01:14:50,291 --> 01:14:51,541
Upravo sam doznala.

739
01:14:52,666 --> 01:14:56,291
Večeras idi sama u hotelsku sobu.

740
01:14:56,375 --> 01:14:58,750
Netko poseban čekat će te ondje.

741
01:15:00,583 --> 01:15:02,000
Netko poseban?

742
01:15:13,125 --> 01:15:14,291
Moj otac?

743
01:15:28,958 --> 01:15:32,791
Marilyn, reci našoj radijskoj publici.
Jesi li usamljena večeras?

744
01:15:34,333 --> 01:15:36,250
Hoćete li se vas dvoje vjenčati?

745
01:15:37,291 --> 01:15:38,291
Vjenčati?

746
01:15:39,791 --> 01:15:40,625
Ne.

747
01:15:59,958 --> 01:16:02,041
Je li ovdje? Moj otac?

748
01:16:04,958 --> 01:16:08,041
Ovo je kao sretan kraj dugog,
zbrkanog filma.

749
01:16:08,125 --> 01:16:09,166
Tvoj otac?

750
01:16:12,083 --> 01:16:14,375
Mislila sam da imam poseban sastanak…

751
01:16:16,041 --> 01:16:18,958
nakon zabave u hotelskoj sobi?

752
01:16:29,708 --> 01:16:34,541
<i>Francuzi vole umirati zbog ljubavi</i>

753
01:16:34,625 --> 01:16:39,458
<i>Oduševljeni su nadmetanjima</i>

754
01:16:40,208 --> 01:16:43,916
<i>Ali ja volim muškarca koji živi</i>

755
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:50,958
<i>I poklanja skupi nakit</i>

756
01:16:51,041 --> 01:16:53,208
<i>Poljubac u ruku</i>

757
01:16:53,291 --> 01:16:56,250
<i>Možda je vrlo europska stvar</i>

758
01:16:56,333 --> 01:16:59,916
<i>Ali dijamanti su ženini</i>
<i>najbolji prijatelji</i>

759
01:17:01,500 --> 01:17:03,958
<i>Poljubac je možda sjajan</i>

760
01:17:04,666 --> 01:17:08,375
<i>Ali neće platiti stanarinu</i>
<i>tvog skromnog stana</i>

761
01:17:09,083 --> 01:17:12,125
<i>Ili ti pomoći kod automata</i>

762
01:17:12,208 --> 01:17:16,875
<i>Muškarci se ohlade kada djevojke ostare</i>

763
01:17:16,958 --> 01:17:21,250
<i>Na kraju izgubimo svoj šarm</i>

764
01:17:22,333 --> 01:17:27,541
<i>Četvrtastog ili kruškolikog oblika</i>
<i>To kamenje ne gubi oblik</i>

765
01:17:27,625 --> 01:17:28,875
<i>Dijamanti su ženini…</i>

766
01:17:28,958 --> 01:17:30,125
O, Tatice.

767
01:17:32,208 --> 01:17:34,541
To na ekranu, nisam to ja.

768
01:17:34,625 --> 01:17:35,625
<i>Tiffany !</i>

769
01:17:39,416 --> 01:17:40,500
<i>Cartier !</i>

770
01:17:43,083 --> 01:17:44,500
<i>Black Starr</i>

771
01:17:44,583 --> 01:17:45,875
<i>Frost Gorham !</i>

772
01:17:45,958 --> 01:17:48,458
<i>Pričaj mi, Harry Winstone</i>
<i>Sve mi ispričaj !</i>

773
01:17:53,541 --> 01:17:58,583
<i>Možda će doći vrijeme</i>
<i>kad će cura trebati odvjetnika</i>

774
01:17:58,666 --> 01:18:02,291
<i>Ali dijamanti su ženini</i>
<i>najbolji prijatelji</i>

775
01:18:08,375 --> 01:18:09,416
Idemo.

776
01:18:22,875 --> 01:18:24,666
Zbog ovoga si ubila dijete?

777
01:19:03,750 --> 01:19:04,750
Tata?

778
01:19:14,375 --> 01:19:15,375
Dušo.

779
01:19:20,791 --> 01:19:21,791
To si ti.

780
01:19:31,458 --> 01:19:32,625
Marilyn, ja…

781
01:19:34,416 --> 01:19:36,125
Samo želim da si sretna.

782
01:19:43,125 --> 01:19:44,375
Sretna sam.

783
01:19:45,875 --> 01:19:47,833
Cijeli sam život sretna.

784
01:19:50,875 --> 01:19:52,375
Marilyn, volimo se.

785
01:19:54,875 --> 01:19:55,958
Vjenčajmo se.

786
01:20:11,250 --> 01:20:12,583
Mislim da jest.

787
01:20:32,583 --> 01:20:34,416
Toliko te volim.

788
01:20:39,250 --> 01:20:41,625
Želim te zaštititi od ovih šakala.

789
01:20:42,666 --> 01:20:44,750
Želim te odvesti daleko od ovoga.

790
01:20:48,208 --> 01:20:49,208
Da.

791
01:20:56,375 --> 01:21:00,916
<i>U tebi novi svijet se rađa</i>

792
01:21:02,291 --> 01:21:03,458
<i>Kao dvoje</i>

793
01:21:05,583 --> 01:21:06,958
<i>Prije tebe…</i>

794
01:21:08,541 --> 01:21:10,083
<i>Postojao je samo jedan</i>

795
01:21:20,083 --> 01:21:21,083
To je sve?

796
01:21:22,333 --> 01:21:23,500
To je cijela pjesma?

797
01:21:25,041 --> 01:21:27,125
-Da.
-Dobra je, dušo.

798
01:21:38,166 --> 01:21:39,791
<i>Ljudi kuhaju špagete?</i>

799
01:21:41,583 --> 01:21:43,416
Ne kupe ih gotove u trgovini?

800
01:21:49,875 --> 01:21:51,416
Slasno miriši.

801
01:21:55,083 --> 01:21:56,000
Mogu li kušati?

802
01:22:04,500 --> 01:22:05,916
Ovo se jede?

803
01:22:06,750 --> 01:22:08,125
Stojeći?

804
01:22:13,416 --> 01:22:15,916
Marilyn, kako je biti filmska zvijezda?

805
01:22:19,041 --> 01:22:21,083
Nisam ja zvijezda.

806
01:22:21,166 --> 01:22:23,000
Ja sam obična plavuša.

807
01:22:24,041 --> 01:22:25,416
Boja kose je prava?

808
01:22:26,208 --> 01:22:27,416
Ne.

809
01:22:38,625 --> 01:22:40,875
<i>Tatice, strašno je</i>

810
01:22:41,625 --> 01:22:44,833
<i>kako scena s pravim ljudima</i>

811
01:22:46,166 --> 01:22:48,791
<i>dugo traje.</i>

812
01:22:49,583 --> 01:22:50,791
Kao na autobusu.

813
01:22:54,208 --> 01:22:55,541
Što će ga zaustaviti?

814
01:22:56,375 --> 01:22:57,208
Ili…

815
01:22:58,875 --> 01:23:02,125
Ili kako shvatiti što ljudi misle

816
01:23:02,208 --> 01:23:04,500
kad najvjerojatnije ne misle ništa.

817
01:23:08,125 --> 01:23:09,458
To nije scenarij.

818
01:23:10,916 --> 01:23:12,375
Nema smisla.

819
01:23:15,000 --> 01:23:16,416
Samo se dogodi.

820
01:23:19,375 --> 01:23:20,791
Kao vrijeme?

821
01:23:26,833 --> 01:23:28,583
Znaš, dušo, u boksu…

822
01:23:30,250 --> 01:23:32,541
kažu: „To mu je privuklo pažnju“,

823
01:23:34,750 --> 01:23:36,416
kada tip dobije jak udarac.

824
01:23:38,250 --> 01:23:42,250
Riječ je o pažnji, dušo. O koncentraciji.

825
01:23:44,000 --> 01:23:45,791
Ako to nemaš, ti…

826
01:24:35,083 --> 01:24:37,125
Mogu vas ozlijediti, pederčine.

827
01:24:43,833 --> 01:24:45,583
To nije ispravan stav.

828
01:24:49,333 --> 01:24:51,583
Mi smo na tvojoj strani.

829
01:24:51,666 --> 01:24:54,708
I daminoj. Ona je prava…

830
01:24:55,291 --> 01:24:56,958
Otmjena dama.

831
01:24:58,291 --> 01:25:01,375
Mi mislimo, snažno,

832
01:25:01,458 --> 01:25:05,250
da te negative treba maknuti s tržišta…

833
01:25:07,000 --> 01:25:10,000
Da ne budu zloupotrijebljeni.

834
01:25:46,833 --> 01:25:47,958
Gdje je, dovraga…

835
01:25:51,083 --> 01:25:53,000
Bok, Tatice. Gdje si bio?

836
01:26:00,541 --> 01:26:03,666
Tatice. Ja sam kriva.

837
01:26:04,833 --> 01:26:08,333
Ne znam kako je soba postala ovakva.
Možda sam bila bolesna.

838
01:26:13,916 --> 01:26:16,916
Te fotografije. To si ti. Meso.

839
01:26:20,166 --> 01:26:21,250
Ne.

840
01:26:23,250 --> 01:26:24,916
Ne želim to biti.

841
01:26:27,416 --> 01:26:28,583
Reci im da nećeš.

842
01:26:29,500 --> 01:26:31,166
Novi film? Nema dogovora.

843
01:26:33,083 --> 01:26:34,750
Tatice, moram raditi.

844
01:26:35,833 --> 01:26:37,250
To je moj život.

845
01:26:39,000 --> 01:26:41,083
Reci im da želiš bolje uloge.

846
01:26:42,333 --> 01:26:44,458
Ozbiljnije uloge. Reci da daješ otkaz.

847
01:26:44,541 --> 01:26:47,458
Reci im da tvoj suprug kaže
da daješ otkaz.

848
01:26:48,416 --> 01:26:49,250
Da.

849
01:26:50,833 --> 01:26:52,500
Reći ću im.

850
01:27:15,500 --> 01:27:18,416
Zar ne vidiš koliko te volim?
Zar ne shvaćaš?

851
01:27:18,500 --> 01:27:19,791
Znam.

852
01:27:21,916 --> 01:27:24,250
Ne mogu podnijeti da se tako ponižavaš.

853
01:27:26,750 --> 01:27:30,458
<i>Na kraju mi je bilo žao stvorenja.</i>

854
01:27:31,708 --> 01:27:32,875
„Žao stvorenja?“

855
01:27:33,916 --> 01:27:36,333
Što si htjela da učini? Oženi se?

856
01:27:36,416 --> 01:27:40,708
Izgledao je zastrašujuće,
ali nije bio posve loš.

857
01:27:41,416 --> 01:27:44,541
Mislim da mu je nedostajalo pažnje.

858
01:27:44,625 --> 01:27:47,791
Osjećaj da ga netko voli, treba i želi.

859
01:27:48,666 --> 01:27:50,416
Zanimljivo gledište.

860
01:27:52,666 --> 01:27:56,791
Osjećaš li povjetarac iz podzemne?
Nije li sjajan?

861
01:27:58,791 --> 01:28:00,750
Ohladi zglobove, zar ne?

862
01:28:03,000 --> 01:28:04,791
Što bi sad bilo zabavno raditi?

863
01:28:05,500 --> 01:28:06,416
Rez!

864
01:29:19,875 --> 01:29:21,375
Nije li sjajan?

865
01:30:39,250 --> 01:30:40,250
Tatice?

866
01:30:45,083 --> 01:30:47,666
Tatice, žao mi je…

867
01:30:48,708 --> 01:30:50,875
-Što si toliko čekao.
-Evo je.

868
01:30:52,958 --> 01:30:54,208
Jesi li ponosna?

869
01:30:55,833 --> 01:30:56,708
Ne.

870
01:30:56,791 --> 01:30:58,208
Jesi li ponosna?

871
01:30:58,291 --> 01:31:00,791
-Tatice, nemoj…
-Ne diraj me.

872
01:31:00,875 --> 01:31:02,166
-Nemoj…
-Jesi li ponosna?

873
01:31:02,250 --> 01:31:04,041
-Je li?
-Ne.

874
01:31:04,125 --> 01:31:06,541
-Sutra radim.
-Svima pokazuješ prepone?

875
01:31:06,625 --> 01:31:08,000
Nemoj.

876
01:31:08,083 --> 01:31:11,333
Misliš da to djeluje na mene?

877
01:31:11,416 --> 01:31:14,583
Svi će znati kakva si jebena kurva!

878
01:31:14,666 --> 01:31:16,250
Ustani!

879
01:31:17,583 --> 01:31:18,708
Jebena kurvo!

880
01:31:19,708 --> 01:31:22,625
Dolazi ovamo!

881
01:31:22,708 --> 01:31:24,541
<i>Moja draga kćeri, Norma Jeane.</i>

882
01:31:26,416 --> 01:31:28,333
<i>Nisam gledao tvoj novi film.</i>

883
01:31:29,666 --> 01:31:32,791
<i>Zbog njegovog</i>
<i>vulgarnog naslova i publiciteta,</i>

884
01:31:32,875 --> 01:31:36,833
<i>ogromnih plakata s tvojim likom</i>
<i>i podignutom haljinom</i>

885
01:31:36,916 --> 01:31:39,416
<i>tako da svi vide tvoju intimu,</i>

886
01:31:39,500 --> 01:31:41,791
<i>nisam želio kupiti kartu.</i>

887
01:31:45,625 --> 01:31:46,458
Jebena…

888
01:31:48,625 --> 01:31:50,583
<i>Htio sam upoznati tvog supruga.</i>

889
01:31:51,375 --> 01:31:53,375
<i>Odavno sam njegov obožavatelj.</i>

890
01:31:54,958 --> 01:31:58,708
<i>Bio sam razočaran</i>
<i>što je tvoj brak s takvim sportašem</i>

891
01:31:58,791 --> 01:32:01,750
<i>završio razvodom i ružnim publicitetom.</i>

892
01:32:04,416 --> 01:32:07,125
<i>Barem nema djece da požanju sramotu.</i>

893
01:32:33,708 --> 01:32:34,750
Moja Magda.

894
01:32:36,250 --> 01:32:38,416
ULAZ NA POZORNICU

895
01:32:38,500 --> 01:32:39,625
<i>Moja Magda.</i>

896
01:32:41,208 --> 01:32:48,166
<i>Magda.</i>

897
01:32:50,916 --> 01:32:52,000
<i>Magda.</i>

898
01:33:40,750 --> 01:33:41,833
Marilyn Monroe?

899
01:33:44,166 --> 01:33:45,083
Ovdje?

900
01:33:47,750 --> 01:33:49,500
Magda? Ona?

901
01:33:50,875 --> 01:33:55,375
„Kad sanjam o onom mjestu,
sanjam o mirisu rublja.“

902
01:33:56,708 --> 01:34:02,500
„Kada se prelijeva, a <i>Magda,</i>
pjesma koju sam napisao, pluta namočena.“

903
01:34:03,416 --> 01:34:05,375
„Panično želim skupiti stranice

904
01:34:05,458 --> 01:34:08,708
prije no što tinta iscuri
i pjesma se raspadne u rukama.“

905
01:34:10,541 --> 01:34:11,875
Zaljubljen je u nju.

906
01:34:12,750 --> 01:34:14,500
„Te riječi za nju…“

907
01:34:14,583 --> 01:34:16,333
„Dvije stotine riječi.“

908
01:34:16,416 --> 01:34:19,208
„Kao molitva.“

909
01:34:21,041 --> 01:34:24,208
„Budim se u Brooklynu,
gotovo 40 godina kasnije,

910
01:34:24,291 --> 01:34:25,916
srce mi udara u grudima.“

911
01:34:27,125 --> 01:34:29,666
„Sjetim se njezinog lica, rumenog,

912
01:34:30,750 --> 01:34:34,416
i njezinih divnih očiju
kako dižu pogled s pjesme i govore…“

913
01:34:40,666 --> 01:34:42,000
Nije moja Magda.

914
01:35:56,375 --> 01:36:03,000
MARILYN MONROE - TOM EWELL
SEDAM GODINA VJERNOSTI

915
01:36:03,083 --> 01:36:05,916
<i>Magda je bila moja prva ljubav.</i>

916
01:36:08,916 --> 01:36:10,416
Nikada konzumirana.

917
01:36:12,541 --> 01:36:14,375
Nikada objavljena.

918
01:36:18,958 --> 01:36:20,208
Bila bi,

919
01:36:21,958 --> 01:36:25,750
da je živa, u srednjim pedesetima.

920
01:36:28,541 --> 01:36:29,791
Predivna Magda.

921
01:36:31,166 --> 01:36:32,125
Sredovječna.

922
01:36:41,833 --> 01:36:42,666
Ja…

923
01:36:43,916 --> 01:36:47,416
imam neke ideje o Magdi,

924
01:36:48,416 --> 01:36:49,708
ako te zanima.

925
01:36:51,875 --> 01:36:53,375
Naravno. Zanima me.

926
01:36:55,791 --> 01:36:57,291
Lijepo od tebe što brineš.

927
01:37:01,708 --> 01:37:07,166
Magda je poput Natashe u <i>Tri sestre.</i>

